list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Set up project structure and initialize key components
This commit establishes the foundational structure for the Adaptive Data Fusion project. It includes TypeScript and Flask configurations, initial backend models and routes, React frontend components, global styling, and test setup. IntelliJ project files and other development environment configurations are also included for streamlined collaboration.
